<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Offline — Kewer</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: #f8f9fa; }
        .icon-offline { font-size: 80px; color: #6c757d; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="text-center p-4">
        <div class="icon-offline">📵</div>
        <h2 class="mt-3">Anda Sedang Offline</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">Koneksi internet tidak tersedia. Data pembayaran yang Anda input akan otomatis disinkronkan saat terhubung kembali.</p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary mt-3" onclick="location.reload()">
            Coba Lagi
        </button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
